Mutane sama da miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron da aka yi wa Brett Kavanaugh
Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka saurari jawabin da mai neman zama Alkalin Kotun Koli, Bret Kavanaugh da Christine Blasey Ford suka yi a tashoshin talabijin shida a ranar Alhamis, a kan zargin da ake yi masa na cin zarafinsa a shekarun 1980.
A halin yanzu, siyasa ta ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin tsaka mai wuya, kuma masu watsa labarai sun katse shirye-shiryen su na yau da kullum da rahotanni game da juyin juya halin ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi, cewa FBI za ta gudanar da binciken mako guda game da tuhumar.
Christine Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa ta tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya taba ta a wani biki a makarantar sakandare, ya sha giya ya kuma yi kokarin cire mata rigarta.
Kavanaugh ya ce a cikin shaidar da ya bayar da farin ciki, ya ce yana da tabbacin cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila mutane fiye da miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli taron, in ji Nielsen.
Kamfanin ya yi lissafin matsakaicin kallon CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Lambar sauran tashoshin da suka watsa bayanan kamar su PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network ba su samu ba nan take.
Kuma Nielsen yawanci yana da matsala wajen lissafin mutanen da suke kallo a ofisoshinsa.
Wannan adadi daidai yake da na masu kallon wasan ƙwallon ƙafa a wasan neman ko kuma na bikin Oscar.
Tashar Fox News Channel, wadda masu gabatar da shirye-shiryen ta ke goyon bayan nadin Kavanaugh, ita ce ta fi kowa kallon tashar, inda Nielsen ta ce, a lokacin zamanta na tsawon yini, an samu masu kallo miliyan 5.69.
Na biyu kuma shi ne ABC da ke da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
Nielsen ya ba da rahoton cewa CBS tana da masu kallo miliyan 3.1, NBC miliyan 2.94, MSNBC miliyan 2.89 da CNN miliyan 2.52.
An ci gaba da nuna sha'awar bayan an kammala tattaunawar.
Babban jarumi na wasan kwaikwayon na ranar Juma'a shi ne Sanata Flake.
Bayan ofishin wannan dan jam'iyyar mai sassaucin ra'ayi ya fitar da sanarwar cewa zai kada kuri'a ga Kavanaugh, kyamarorin CNN da CBS sun kama shi da safiyar Juma'a ana yi masa ihu yayin da yake shirin hawa lif zuwa taron kwamitin shari'a.
CNN ta watsa shi a kai tsaye, yana tsaye na 'yan mintoci yana rufe idanunsa yana jin an zage shi.
Wata mata ta ce, "Ina tsaye a gabanku".
"Kuna tsammani yana faɗin gaskiya ga ƙasar?"
Na kuma ji, "Ka yi ƙarfi, amma mata da yawa ba su da ƙarfi".
Flake ya ce ofishinsa ya fitar da sanarwa, kuma kafin a rufe kofar lif, ya kara da cewa zai ce ƙarin bayani a taron kwamitin.
Daga baya, duk tashoshin talabijin da na USB sun watsa kai tsaye lokacin da aka shirya cewa kwamitin shari'a su yi zabe kan gabatar da takarar Kavanaugh don kada kuri'ar majalisar dattawa.
Amma Flake ya ce zai yi hakan ne kawai idan har FBI ta bincika zargin da ake yi wa dan takarar a mako mai zuwa, abin da 'yan Democrat suka bukaci.
Flake ya yi ta tattaunawa da abokinsa, dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Democrat Chris Coons.
Bayan tattaunawa da Coons da wasu 'yan majalisar dattawa, Flake ya yanke shawara.
Flake ya yi zabe mai muhimmanci domin ya bayyana cewa ba tare da bincike ba, 'yan Republican ba za su samu kuri'un da za su amince da Kavanaugh ba.
Shugaba Trump ya kaddamar da bincike kan zargin da aka yi wa Kavanaugh.
