A cewar mai zuba jari kuma masanin ilimin kere kere Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple, kasar Sin na kara shiga harkar kere kere (AI) kuma ya kamata Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take kashewa wajen bincike a fannin.
Wannan tsokaci ya zo ne bayan da bangarori daban-daban na gwamnatin Amurka suka fitar da sanarwar AI, duk da cewa Amurka baki daya ba ta da wata dabara ta musamman game da ilimin kere kere.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta kaddamar da wani shiri a bara, inda take son ta zama kasa ta farko a fannin kirkirar kere kere ta hanyar fasaha a shekarar 2030.
"Haɗa kasafin kuɗi na bincike na AI zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, saboda duk sauran ƙasashe sun yi nesa da Amurka kuma muna neman ƙarin ci gaba a AI", in ji Lee.
A cikin wata hira da CNBC, Lee ya ce ninka yawan kudaden da ake bayarwa zai iya ninka yiwuwar cewa babbar sabuwar sabuwar fasahar kere kere za ta faru a Amurka.
Lee, wanda ya wallafa littafinsa mai suna "Superpowers of AI: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" a watan nan a Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne shugaban kamfanin Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI a kasar Sin, Face++.
A Carnegie Mellon University a shekarun 1980s, ya yi aiki a kan tsarin AI wanda ya wuce mafi kyawun ɗan wasan Amurka a wasan Othello, kuma daga baya ya zama babban jami'in bincike na Microsoft da shugaban kamfanin Google na China.
Lee ya yaba da gasar fasahar gwamnatin Amurka da ta gabata, kamar gasar Robotics Challenge ta Hukumar Ci Gaban Bincike ta Defense, kuma ya tambayi lokacin da za a sake yin wani don taimakawa gano sabbin masu hangen nesa.
Lee ya ce masu bincike a Amirka suna yawan neman tallafin gwamnati.
"Kasuwancin masana kimiyya ba ya zuwa daga China, kamfanoni ne", in ji Lee.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun yi amfani da manyan masana a jami'o'i a cikin 'yan shekarun nan don yin aiki a kan ilimin kere kere.
Don inganta kokarin AI, Lee ya ce, Amurka na iya samun taimako ta hanyar sauya manufofinta na shige da fice.
"A ganina, ya kamata a ba da katin kore ga masu samun digirin digirgir a fannin AI", in ji shi.
Majalisar Jiha ta kasar Sin ta fitar da Shirin Ci gaban Artificial Intelligence na Sabuwar Zamani a watan Yulin 2017.
Gidauniyar Kimiyya ta kasa ta kasar Sin tana ba da kudade ga masu ilimi a irin yadda hukumar kimiyya ta kasa da sauran hukumomin gwamnati ke ba da kudade ga masu bincike a Amurka, amma ingancin aikin ilimi a kasar Sin ya fi muni, in ji Lee.
Ma'aikatar tsaron Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar hadin gwiwa kan ilimin kere kere a wannan shekarar, don hada kan masana'antu da masana ilimi, kuma fadar White House ta sanar da kafa kwamitin zabe kan ilimin kere kere.
Kuma DARPA ta sanar a wannan watan cewa za ta zuba dala biliyan biyu a wani shiri da ake kira AI Next.
