Trump ya yi jawabi a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
A wannan maraice, a birnin Wheeling, a jihar West Virginia, Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara wani gagarumin jawabi na kamfen.
Wannan shi ne na farko cikin taro biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau kamar su Tennessee da Mississippi.
A yayin da aka dakatar da zaben tabbatar da dan takararsa na kujerar da ta rage a kotun koli, Trump na son samun goyon baya a zaben da ke tafe a tsakiyar wa'adinsa, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar asarar majalisa a zaben na watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne jawabin Trump zai fara, kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallonsa a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, da ƙarfe bakwai na yammacin yammacin ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube a ƙasa.
Trump zai yi magana ne a kan sauraron wanda ya tsaya takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya gudana a wannan makon kuma ya kasance mai matukar damuwa game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i, ana sa ran za a dage zaben tabbatar da kujerar majalisa na tsawon mako guda kafin a fara binciken FBI.
Amma babban dalilin wannan taro shi ne don taimaka wa 'yan Republican su ci gaba da yin aiki kafin zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters ya ce, masu shirya kamfen din Shugaba Trump sun ce, taron na biyar na mako mai zuwa, na nufin "karfafawa masu aikin sa kai da masu goyon bayan jam'iyyar, domin 'yan Republican su yi kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai".
"Sanin cewa majalisar dattawa tana da muhimmanci a ajandar shugaban kasa, shi ya sa shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da dama a wannan kakar zaben", in ji mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda bai so a bayyana sunansa ba.
Jaridar Metro News ta West Virginia ta ce masu goyon bayan taron na yau a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling na iya zuwa daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ana iya kallon taron a Pittsburgh.
A ranar Asabar, wannan ne karo na biyu da Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia a cikin wata daya, inda ya samu sama da kashi 40 cikin dari na kuri'un da ya kada a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia Patrick Morrissey wanda ke kasa a zaben.
"Ba abu mai kyau ba ne ga Morrissey cewa shugaban kasa ya zo ya taimaka masa a binciken", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a jami'ar West Virginia.
