Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup
Turai za ta samu dama mai kyau a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup bayan da ta yi nasara a wasannin biyu da biyu a ranar Asabar da ci gaba 10-6 a kan Amurka.
Wani dan wasa mai suna Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari, wanda aka ce ya yi kusa da cin Tiger Woods sau biyu, sun yanke shawarar yin kwallo hudu a Le Golf National.
Ƙungiyar Turai da Thomas Bjorn suka yi amfani da su don su riƙe kofin da suka rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, sun mamaye wasannin ƙwallon ƙafa biyu da safe tare da ƙungiyar Amurka, wanda ya ci nasara 3-1.
Amurka ta nuna juriya a wasanni hudu, ta ci biyu, amma ba ta iya shiga cikin rashin isasshen kuɗi ba.
Jam'iyyar Jim Furyke na bukatar maki takwas a wasanni 12 da suka yi a ranar Lahadi domin ta ci nasara.
Fleetwood shine farkon dan wasan Turai da ya ci maki hudu a jere, yayin da shi da Molinari, wanda aka yi wa lakabi da "Molliwood" bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki, sun zama ma'aurata na biyu da suka ci maki hudu daga wasanninsu na farko a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan da suka doke Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan kwallon kafa biyu, sai suka doke Woods da dan wasan Amurka na farko, Bryson Dechambeau, da ci 5 da 4.
Woods, wanda ya yi wasa biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna wasu 'yan wasan da suka fi kyau, amma yanzu ya yi rashin nasara 19 daga cikin wasanni 29 da ya buga a wasan biyu-da-biyu da kuma bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ya huta daga wasan kwallon biyu na safiyar yau, ya koma tare da abokin wasan Henrik Stenson a wasan biyu a 2&1 da Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka - na farko da na uku a cikin jerin duniya.
Amma a wannan rana mai kyau da ke kudu maso yammacin Paris, Turai ba ta da nasara.
Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas sun ci biyu a raga a ranar Asabar.
Sun sami nasara 2&1 mai wuya akan Mutanen Espanya Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter a wasan kwando biyu kuma sun dawo daga baya don doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4&3 a wasan biyu, duk da cewa ya rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin Ryder Cup da wata kungiya ta koma daga rashin ci hudu zuwa wasan biyu, duk da cewa a matsayin mai kare Furyk's side kawai yana buƙatar tsallakewa don samun kofin.
Bayan ranar biyu ta zama mafi kyau a cikin kwanaki biyu, kamar dai ranar Lahadi ta sake dawowa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta daina makamai ba a kowane hali ba, ba tare da amincewa ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya ce a ranar Asabar, takunkumin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya na ci gaba da kara tsananta musu kan Amurka, kuma a irin wannan yanayi, kasar ba za ta taba barin makaman nukiliyarta ba.
Ri Yong Ho ya ce a babban taronsa na shekara-shekara cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "matakan kirki" a cikin shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da makaman rokoki, da kuma kawar da wuraren gwajin nukiliya, da kuma alkawarin da ta yi na cewa ba za ta yada makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya ba.
"Amma ba mu ga wani irin martani daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, babu amincewa da tsaron kasa, kuma a irin wannan yanayi, ba zai yiwu a kawar da makamai ba".
Yayin da Ri ya maimaita sanannun korafe-korafen Koriya ta Arewa game da kin amincewa da Washington ga tsarin "matakai" na kawar da makaman nukiliya, inda ake cewa za a biya Koriya ta Arewa lada a kowane mataki, ya bayyana cewa yana da muhimmanci a cikin cewa bai yi watsi da kawar da makaman nukiliya ba saboda Pyongyang ta riga ta fuskanta a baya.
Ri ya yi magana game da sanarwar hadin gwiwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka yi a taron farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga Yuni, inda Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki kan "yanke makaman nukiliya daga yankin Koriya" yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbatar da tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa na neman kawo karshen yakin da ta yi a shekarun 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta fara ba da makaman nukiliya.
Har ila yau, Washington ta yi tsayayya da kira na sassauta takunkumin kasa da kasa mai tsanani kan Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta nace kan "yanke makaman nukiliya da farko" kuma tana kara matsa lamba kan takunkumin don aiwatar da burinta, har ma tana adawa da "yanke karshen yaki", in ji Ri.
"Halin da muke ciki na ganin cewa takunkumi zai iya kawo mu ga kasa, mafarki ne na mutanen da ba su san kome ba game da mu.
Matsalar ita ce, ci gaba da takunkumi yana kara sa mu cikin rashin amincewa.
Ri bai ambaci shirin taron Kim da Trump na biyu ba, wanda shugaban Amurka ya yi magana a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon nan.
Maimakon haka, ministan ya yi nuni da ganawar Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in sau uku a cikin watanni biyar, ya kara da cewa: Idan Koriya ta Kudu ce ke da hannu a wannan batun na kawar da makaman nukiliya ba Amurka ba, ba za a sami irin wannan matsalar ba. 
Amma, sautin jawabin Ri ya sha bambam da na shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da ya fada wa babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa harin makaman nukiliya na Koriya ta Arewa a Amurka ya zama dole bayan da muguwar Shugaba Trump ta kira Kim a matsayin dan makamin nukiliya na kai hari.
A Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a wannan shekara, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar "hallaka Koriya ta Arewa gaba daya", ya yaba wa Kim saboda ƙarfin zuciyarsa na ɗaukar matakan kawar da makaman, amma ya ce har yanzu akwai aiki da yawa da za a yi, kuma takunkumi dole ne su kasance har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da lokacin da zai yi hakan, ya ce: "Ko shekara biyu, ko uku, ko watanni biyar - ba kome".
China da Rasha sun ce ya kamata kwamitin sulhu na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya ba Pyongyang lada saboda matakan da ta dauka.
Amma, a ranar Alhamis, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya shaida wa Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa, "Shari'ar takunkumin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya dole ne ta ci gaba da karfi ba tare da tsayawa ba har sai mun fahimci cikakken, karshe, tabbatar da kawar da makaman nukiliya".
Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya amince da takunkumin da aka kafa kan Koriya ta Arewa tun 2006 domin hana Pyongyang samun kudade don ayyukan nukiliya da kuma makamai masu linzami.
Pompeo da Ri sun gana a babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a gefe, kuma Pompeo ya ce zai ziyarci Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekara, amma tafiyarsa ta karshe ba ta ƙare da kyau ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana mai cewa an samu ci gaba, sai dai a cikin 'yan sa'o'i Koriya ta Arewa ta ce yana da 'yan ta'adda.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin ganawa da Moon a wannan watan don ta rushe sansanin makaman nukiliya da kuma na nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki matakan da suka dace.
Ya ce Kim ya sanar da shi cewa "matakan da ya ke fatan samu sune tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore, kuma yana kan hanyar daidaita dangantakarsa da Washington.
Daliban Harvard sun halarci wani darasi da ya koya musu yadda za su samu isashen hutu
Wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard a wannan shekara ya sa dukkan dalibansa su kara yin barci, a kokarin da suke yi na yaki da al'adar karatu na dare da dare, inda dalibai ke yin bacci da kuma sha da maganin kafeyin.
Masu ilimi sun gano cewa ɗalibai a jami'a mafi girma a duniya sau da yawa ba su da tabbaci game da yadda za su kula da kansu.
An tsara wannan darasi ne da Charles Czeisler, Farfesa a fannin maganin bacci a Makarantar Likita ta Harvard da kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da kuma Asibitin Mata, wanda ya yi imanin cewa shi ne na farko a cikin irin wannan asibitin a Amurka.
Ya fara wannan darasi ne bayan ya yi jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci a kan ilmantarwa.
A ƙarshe, wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta ce, "Me ya sa ba za ka gaya mini wannan ba sai yanzu, a shekarar karshe ta?"
Ta ce ba a taɓa gaya mata muhimmancin barci ba, abin da ya ba ni mamaki, in ji shi a cikin The Telegraph.
Wannan darasi da aka fara gabatar da shi a wannan shekara, yana ba wa ɗalibai muhimman bayanai game da yadda yin barci da kyau yake taimaka wa ɗalibai su yi nasara a makaranta da kuma wasanni, kuma yana inganta lafiyarsu.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar dan adam a Harvard Medical School kuma shugaban jami'ar kiwon lafiya, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan darasi ne bayan da ta gano cewa dalibai sun yi rashin bacci sosai a cikin mako guda.
Darasi na awa ɗaya ya ƙunshi ayyuka masu yawa da za a yi ta yin amfani da su.
Wani sashe na hoton makarantar sakandare inda ɗalibai ke danna kofuna na kofi, labule, takalma, da littattafai game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da kuma yadda rashin barci da muhimmancin halayen bacci masu kyau ke shafar wasan motsa jiki.
A wani sashe kuma, an koya wa masu halarta yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya ƙara haɗarin ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar da ke ɗauke da gumaka masu ma'ana tana sa masu halarta su yi tunani game da yadda suke yin rayuwarsu.
Mun san cewa halin ɗalibai ba zai canza nan take ba.
Amma muna ganin suna da hakkin su sani - kamar yadda kuke da hakkin ku san illar shan sigari a kan lafiyarku", in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Al'adar alfahari da "karshen dare" har yanzu tana nan, ya kara da cewa, fasahar zamani da kuma karuwar matsin lamba kan dalibai na nufin matsalar rashin bacci na karuwa.
Ya ce samun isasshen bacci ya kamata ya zama "makamin sirri" na dalibi wajen yaki da damuwa da gajiya da kuma damuwa, har ma don kaucewa samun karin nauyi, domin rashin bacci yana mayar da kwakwalwa cikin yanayin yunwa, don haka mutum yana ci gaba da jin yunwa.
Raymond So, wani ɗalibi ɗan shekara 19 da ke California da ke nazarin kimiyyar halitta da kuma ilimin lissafi, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler ya tsara darasi da ɗaya daga cikin ɗalibansa ya koya a shekara ta ƙarshe a Harvard.
Ya ce wannan darasi ya sa ya soma tunani sosai kuma ya motsa shi ya ci gaba da karatun.
Yana fatan cewa mataki na gaba shi ne ya nemi dukkan daliban da suka kammala karatun digiri su kammala irin wannan shirin kafin su shiga wata cibiyar gasa.
Farfesan ya shawarci ɗaliban su yi la'akari da saita ƙararrawa a lokacin da za su yi barci da kuma lokacin da za su farka, kuma su san cewa hasken da ke fitowa daga allon lantarki da kuma hasken LED zai iya shafar motsin zuciyarmu, kuma hakan zai iya sa mu yi barci.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: Goal na Meng ya jefa Gerrard cikin wani mummunan rauni
Rangers sun sake shan kashi, lokacin da harbi na Dolly Menga ya tabbatar da rashin jin daɗin Steven Gerrard a cikin rashin nasara 1-0 a Livingston.
Ibrox sun yi kokarin samun nasarar farko daga ranar 4 zuwa 1 ga watan Fabrairu a St Johnstone, amma kungiyar Gary Holt ta yi nasarar doke Gerrard a wasanni 18 a matsayin kocin, inda ya bar shi a matsayi na takwas daga shugabannin Ladbrokes Premiership Hearts.
Mengo ya buga minti bakwai kafin a tashi daga wasa kuma tawagar Rangers ba ta da kwarin gwiwa da kuma niyyar daidaitawa.
Yayin da Rangers suka koma na shida, Livingston ya hau na uku kuma ya yi kusa da Hibernian da ci daya.
Kuma za a iya samun karin matsaloli a Rangers bayan da aka yi wa alkalin wasan Calum Spence jinya saboda raunin da ya samu a kan kansa bayan da aka yi masa barazanar cewa wani abu ne ya buge shi daga filin wasa.
Gerrard ya yi sau takwas a kan tawagarsa da ta yi tsalle ta wuce Ayr zuwa wasan kusa da na karshe na gasar cin kofin Betfred.
A gefe guda kuma, Holt yana tafiya da Livi 11 wanda ya ci Points Hearts a makon da ya gabata kuma zai yi farin ciki da yadda tawagarsa da aka horar da su ta shawo kan abokan hamayyarsu a kowane mataki.
Rangers sun iya sarrafa hannun, amma Livingston ya yi fiye da shi a kan kwallon.
Ya kamata a ci kwallo ne da minti biyu bayan da aka fara wasa, lokacin da Mengo ya fara barin Scott Pittman a kan Allan McGregor, amma dan wasan ya binne babbar damarsa.
Keagan Jacobs ya yi nasara a wasan, amma abokin wasansa Alan Lithgow ya yi nasara a wasan.
Rangers sun dauki iko, amma a cikin kashi na karshe, akwai fatan da yawa fiye da imani.
Alfredo Morelos ya ji cewa ya kamata a yi masa hukuncin daurin awa 15 a lokacin da ya yi karo da Steven Lawless, amma mai wasan kwaikwayo Steven Thomson ya kawar da ƙalubalen Colombia daga teburin.
Rangers sun yi harbi biyu ne kawai a wasan farko, amma tsohon dan wasan Ibrox Liam Kelly ya yi mamakin ci gaban Lassan Coulibaly da kuma Ovie Ejaria.
Duk da cewa Livi ya fara wasa a minti 34 da wasa, babu wanda zai iya musanta cewa sun cancanci hakan saboda sun yi aiki tuƙuru.
Rangers sun sake kasawa da Jacobs a cikin saitin da ya yi zurfi.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya tura kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya kasance mai nutsuwa kuma ya ɗauki Mengo don samun sauƙi.
Gerrard ya kama aiki a lokacin hutu kuma ya maye gurbin Coulibaly da Ryan Kent kuma canjin ya kasance kusan nan take lokacin da gefen ya shiga cikin Morelos, amma Kelly mai ban mamaki ya yi ta fama da layin kuma ya toshe harin.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da jawo masu kallo zuwa wasan da suke so, inda Lithgow da Halkett suka jefa dogon kwallon daya bayan daya.
Holt ya iya zurfafa sahunsa a ƙarshen lokacin, amma McGregor ya tsaya da kyau don toshe Jacobs kafin Litgow ya gudu daga kusurwa.
Mai maye gurbin Rangers Glenn Middleton ya sake samun damar yin hukunci bayan ya yi rikici da Jacobs, amma Thomson ya sake kaucewa.
Almanach: Masu kirkirar na'urar karanta Geiger
Yanzu kuma shafi na mujallarmu ta Lahadi: Satumba 30 ga watan Satumba, 1882, shekara 136 da ta shige, kuma har yanzu ana ci gaba da ƙarawa... ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi na nan gaba Johannes Wilhelm Hans Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta gano da kuma auna radiyo, abin da ya kai ga na'urar da ake kira Geiger Reader.
A lokacin, geiger counter ya zama babban cibiyar al'adun gargajiya, kamar yadda aka nuna a fim din 1950 mai suna "Bells of Coronado", wanda ya ƙunshi masu bincike Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: "Mece ce wannan?"
Rogers:  Wannan na'urar karanta Geiger ce da ake amfani da ita wajen gano ma'adanai masu aikin rediyo kamar uranium.
Idan ka saka waɗannan na'urorin, za ka iya jin tasirin da atom ɗin da ke da rediyo ke yi a cikin ma'adanai.
Evans: "Yau, yanzu ya yi nasara sosai!"
Hans Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, 'yan kwanaki kafin ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
Amma abin da ya yi ya ci gaba da rayuwa.
Sabuwar rigakafin cutar kansa na iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar jikinmu ta "ga" ƙwayoyin cuta
Wani sabon maganin rigakafin cutar kansa zai iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar jikin mutum ya gane kwayoyin cutar kuma ya kashe su.
Rigakafin yana koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki gane ƙwayoyin cuta masu haɗari a matsayin wani ɓangare na magani
Wannan hanyar tana ɗauke da ƙwayar cuta daga jikin mutum kuma a yi amfani da ita a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje
Sai kuma su iya ganin furotin da ke da alaƙa da yawancin ƙwayoyin cuta, sannan su sake yin allurar.
Rigakafin gwaji yana nuna kyakkyawan sakamako a cikin marasa lafiya da ke da nau'ikan cututtukan daji da yawa.
Wata mata da aka yi mata maganin da ke koya wa jikinta yadda zai gane ƙwayoyin cuta masu haɗari, ta sami sauƙi daga ciwon daji na ƙwanƙwasawa na tsawon watanni 18.
Wannan hanya ta ƙunshi cire ƙwayoyin cuta daga cikin marasa lafiya, canza su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje, don su iya ganin furotin da ake kira HER2 wanda ke faruwa a yawancin cututtukan daji, sannan a sake saka su cikin ƙwayoyin.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky na Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon Ciwon daji ta Amirka a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce: "Bincikenmu ya nuna cewa mun samu riga-kafi mai kyau".
HER2 tana sarrafa ci gaban wasu nau'o'in ciwon daji, ciki har da ciwon nono, na ovarian, na huhu da kuma ciwon daji na colorectal, in ji Farfesa Berzofsky.
Irin wannan tsarin, inda ake cire kwayoyin garkuwar jiki daga marasa lafiya kuma a koya musu su yi amfani da su wajen magance cutar sankarar bargo, an riga an yi amfani da shi wajen maganin cutar sankarar bargo.
Kanye West ya halarci jawabin goyon bayan Trump, a cikin hatinsa na sihiri, bayan ya fito a SNL.
