Bayan ya rera waka ta uku a daren, mai suna "Ghost Town", inda ya saka hat ɗin "Make America Great Again", sai ya fara tofa wa 'yan Democrat baya, ya kuma sake jaddada goyon bayansa ga Shugaba Trump.
"Na kan yi magana da fararen fata, kuma suna cewa, 'Yaya za ka so Trump, idan shi dan wariyar launin fata ne?'
