SNL ta fara wani shiri na satar mutane da Matt Damon a matsayin babban jarumin Hollywood wanda ya yi wa shaidar Bret Kavanaugh ba'a a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa game da zargin fyade da aka yi wa Christine Blasey Ford.
