Game of Thrones star Kit Harington ya shiga cikin wani nau'i na maza da ke da guba
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin Jon Snow da takobi a hannun sa a cikin mummunan wasan kwaikwayo na HBO na zamanin da.
Amma, dan wasan, mai shekara 31, ya yi watsi da ra'ayin cewa jarumawa suna da 'yanci, ya ce irin wannan rawar a kan allo na nufin cewa matasa maza suna jin cewa dole ne su kasance masu ƙarfi don samun girmamawa.
Ya gaya wa jaridar The Sunday Times Culture Kit cewa yana ganin akwai wani abu da ba daidai ba, kuma ya tambayi yadda za a magance matsalar cutarwa ta maza a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri tauraruwarsa ta Star of Thrones Rose Leslie, mai shekaru 31, ya yarda cewa yana da "ƙarfin magana" game da wannan matsalar.
