HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton karuwar sabbin kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14%
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar mutane 14 cikin 100 da ke rayuwa da cutar HIV da AIDS.
A kasar, an kiyasta cewa mutane sama da 820,000 ne ke dauke da cutar.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018, an samu sabbin mutane kusan 40,000 da aka samu.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun kamu da jima'i, wanda ya nuna canji daga baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa ta wasu sassan kasar Sin ta hanyar kamuwa da jini.
Amma adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan sifili, in ji likitocin kasar Sin a wani taron da aka yi a lardin Yunnan.
Yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a China ya karu da mutane 100,000 a kowace shekara.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i na da matukar damuwa a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An yi wa luwadi yancin yin jima'i a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma ana zargin cewa nuna wariya ga LGBT har yanzu yana da yawa.
Bisa ga ra'ayin mazan jiya na ƙasar, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70-90 na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza suna yin aure da mata.
Yawancin cututtuka da ake samu daga jima'i suna zuwa ne daga rashin kāriya a lokacin jima'i.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da hanyoyin magance cutar HIV ga kowa a kasar, a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa ma'aikatanta sun saki bayanan 'yan majalisar dattijai na GOP, tana mai cewa "karya ce mai hadari" da kuma "ka'idar makirci".
A ranar Asabar, 'yar majalisar dokokin Amurka Maxine Waters ta yi tir da zargin cewa wani ma'aikaciyarta ya tura bayanan sirri na 'yan majalisar dattijai uku na Republican zuwa shafin yanar gizon 'yan majalisa.
'Yar Democrat a birnin Los Angeles ta ce masu bincike da kuma shafukan yanar gizo na 'yan adawa sun goyi bayan zargin.
"Ƙarya, ƙarya da sauran ƙazantar ƙarya", in ji Waters a cikin sanarwar ta a shafin Twitter.
An ce bayanan da aka fitar sun haɗa da adireshin gida da kuma lambobin waya na 'yan majalisar dattawa Lindsey Graham na South Carolina da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka biyu na Utah.
Bayanan sun bayyana a shafin yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, kuma wani mutum ne ya wallafa su a Capitol Hill a lokacin da majalisar dattawa ke sauraron karar da aka yi wa mai neman kujerar kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, game da zargin cin zarafin mata.
An samu wannan bayanan ne bayan wasu 'yan majalisar dattijai uku sun yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun sanar da cewa adireshin IP ɗin da ya samo asali daga wannan sakon yana da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma sun ba da bayanin game da ma'aikatan Waters, in ji Hill.
"Wannan da'awar ba ta da tushe kuma ba gaskiya ba ce kuma karya ce", Waters ya ci gaba.
Majalisarmu, wanda aka yi wa barazanar mutuncinsa da kuma bayanansa, saboda zargin da ake yi masa na yaudara da kuma karya, ba ta da alhakin ɓarnatar da bayanan.
Wannan da'awar da babu tushe ba gaskiya ba ce kuma karya ce.
Sanarwar Waters ta yi sanadin zargi a shafukan intanet, ciki har da na tsohon sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙin yarda yana da fushi", in ji Fleischer.
"Wannan ya nuna cewa ba shi da halin zama a majalisa".
Idan aka zargi mutum da abin da bai yi ba, kada ka yi fushi.
Ba za su yi tawaye ba.
Bai kamata ya yi shakkar dalilin da ya sa mai gabatar da kara ya yi hakan ba.
Dole ne su kasance masu natsuwa kuma kada su damu.
Fleischer ya yi kama da yadda Waters ya amsa da sukar da 'yan Democrat suka yi wa mai shari'a Kavanaugh, wanda suka soki saboda ya yi fushi sosai a lokacin sauraron shari'ar ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar Republican, wanda ya yi takara a zaben da Waters, shi ma ya bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafin Twitter.
"Idan gaskiya ne, zai zama wani abu", ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter.
A cikin sanarwar da ta bayar, Waters ta ce ofishinta ya sanar da hukumomi da hukumomin shari'a masu dacewa game da waɗannan da'awar na yaudara.
"Za mu tabbatar da cewa an gano masu laifin", ta ci gaba, "kuma za su dauki alhakin duk wani abin da suka aikata, wanda ke da lahani da kuma hadari ga kowa da kowa da kuma dukkan ma'aikatan na".
Johnny English ya sake yin tsokaci  Ƙaramin ɗan leƙen asiri Rowan Atkinson
Ya zama al'ada a nemi Brexit a kowane sabon fim na Burtaniya, wanda kuma ya zama kamar yadda aka sake farfado da Johnny English a cikin jerin wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo - wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma an dawo da shi cikin 2011 tare da Johnny English Reborn.
Wannan mummunan satire ne akan yadda muke da mummunan al'umma, sabon damarmu ta fitarwa?
Ko ta yaya, wannan ɗan iska, Johnny English mai banƙyama da fuskar roba ya sami lasisinsa don sake yin abubuwa a cikin sabon salo - sunan da ya fi kowane abu da alama cewa babban aikin wasan kwaikwayo ne wanda aka tsara don masu sauraron fim ɗin da ba sa jin Turanci.
Shi ne, ba shakka, wannan ɗan ɓoye mai ɓoye wanda, duk da ƙididdigar da ya yi na smoothie glamour, yana da ɗan ɗan Inspector Clouseau, ɗan ɗan Mr. Bean, da kuma babban ɗan ɗan adam wanda ya buga sautin guda ɗaya a cikin waƙar Chariots of Fire a bikin buɗe wasannin Olympics na London na 2012.
Har ila yau, asalin asalin asalin shi ne mai tafiya da kuma wani mutum mai ban mamaki na duniya, wanda Atkinson ya taɓa yin fim a cikin tallan TV da aka manta da shi na Barclaycard, wanda ya bar rikici a baya.
Akwai abubuwa masu kyau da yawa a cikin wannan fitowar ta ƙarshe.
Na so Johnny English yana zuwa wurin jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu da makamai na zamanin da kuma na ɗan lokaci, mashigar rotor tana rataye kan kwalkwali.
Kyautar Atkinson ta wasan kwaikwayo ta jiki tana kan nuni, amma wasan kwaikwayo yana jin ɗan ƙarami kuma ba shi da mahimmanci, musamman ma lokacin da manyan kamfanonin fim kamar 007 da Mission Impossible yanzu suna ba da wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin wani ɓangare na samar da su.
Abin dariya ya fi dacewa da yara fiye da manya, kuma a gare ni, waƙar Johnny English tana da basira da kuma maida hankali kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi a fim din Mr. Bean.
Wani abu da ake yawan cewa shi ne, Birtaniya na cikin matsala.
Wani dan gwanin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin wani shafin yanar gizo na 'yan leken asiri na Birtaniya, ya kuma gano duk wani jami'in Birtaniya da ke wurin, abin da ya ba wa wani jami'in tsaro tsoro, wani aiki ne da bai kai na Kevin Eldon ba.
Wannan shi ne na karshe ga Firayim Minista, wanda yake da ban mamaki da kuma son zuciya, wanda ya riga ya sha wahala daga cikakken rushewar rashin sha'awar siyasa: Emma Thompson ta yi wasa da wannan hali mai ban sha'awa Theresa May ta yi, amma babu wani abu a cikin rubutun.
Masu ba ta shawara a kan harkokin yawon bude ido sun gaya mata cewa idan aka yi wa kowane ɗan leken asirinta barazana, za ta bukaci a mayar da wani daga aikin.
Wannan yana nufin cewa Johnny English da kansa, wanda yanzu yake aiki a matsayin darektan wani kayan aiki na alatu, amma kuma yana koyar da darussan da suka fi girma game da yadda za a zama mai ba da labari: a nan akwai wasu kyawawan abubuwa, domin English yana ba da makarantar leken asiri kamar Makarantar Rock.
Turanci ya koma Whitehall don sanarwar gaggawa kuma ya sadu da tsohon abokin aikinsa mai shekaru da yawa Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake buga shi.
Bough yanzu ya yi aure, yana zama tare da kwamandan jirgin ruwan, wanda yake da sha'awar, wanda Vicki Pepperdine ta iya ɓata ɗan ƙaramin ƙarfinta.
Don haka Batman da Robin, a cikin aikin da suke yi wa asirin Sarauniya, sun sake dawowa cikin aiki kuma sun sadu da kyakkyawar femme fatale Ophelia Bullet, wanda Olga Kurylenko ta buga.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista ta yi kasala ga wata jaruma mai karfin fasaha mai karfin gaske, wanda ke da'awar cewa zai iya warware laifin cyber na Birtaniya: Jason Volta, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
English da Bough sun fara tafiyarsu da abubuwan ban dariya: suna ɓoye kamar masu jiran abinci suna ƙona gidan cin abinci na Faransa; suna haifar da rikici yayin da suke shiga cikin jirgin ruwan Volt na alfarma; kuma English ya haifar da rashin tsari na gaske yayin da yake ƙoƙarin yin amfani da gaskiyar ta hanyar shiga cikin gidan Volt.
Dukkanin 'yan wasan ace sun shirya don wannan wasan karshe, amma duk da cewa tana da kyau da kuma tashin hankali, tana da wani abu na talabijin na yara.
Wannan abu ne mai kyau.
Kamar yadda na yi a sauran fina-finan Johnny English, sai na yi tunani: Shin masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya ba za ta iya ba Rowan Atkinson rawar da ta dace da baiwarsa ba?
Labour sun musanta cewa za su ci gaba da shirin ga Englishman su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako don samun biya a cikin kwanaki biyar
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn za ta yi la'akari da wani tsari na musamman inda za a ba wa 'yan Birtaniya aiki kwana hudu a mako kuma a biya su biyar.
Jam'iyyar ta ce tana son shugabannin kamfanoni su ba ma'aikata kudin da za su samu ta hanyar amfani da fasahar kere kere (AI).
Ma'aikata za su ji daɗin hutun mako uku - amma za su ci gaba da samun albashi iri ɗaya.
Majiyoyi sun ce wannan ra'ayin zai dace da tsarin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar kuma tana shirin karkatar da kasar ga ma'aikata.
An amince da sauyawar zuwa mako hudu na aiki a taron kungiyoyin kwadago a matsayin hanyar da ma'aikata za su iya amfani da tattalin arziki mai sauyawa.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Labour mai shekaru da yawa ya shaida wa jaridar Sunday Times cewa: "Ana sa ran za a sanar da kimanta wannan matakin a karshen shekara.
Ba za a yi wannan ba dare ɗaya, amma hutun kwana huɗu na aiki abu ne da ya dace da ra'ayin jam'iyyar na daidaita tattalin arziki a kan ma'aikata da kuma tsarin masana'antar jam'iyyar gaba ɗaya.
Jam'iyyar Labour ba za ta kasance farkon wanda ya goyi bayan wannan ra'ayin ba, jam'iyyar Green Party ta yi alkawarin mako hudu na aiki a lokacin yakin neman zaben 2017.
Amma a halin yanzu, jam'iyyar Labour ba ta amince da wannan burin ba.
Mai magana da yawun jam'iyyar Labour ya ce, "Ranar aiki ta kwana hudu ba manufa ba ce ta jam'iyyarmu, kuma ba ta da muhimmanci a cikinta".
Shadow Chancellor John McDonnell ya yi amfani da taron ma'aikata na makon da ya gabata don aiwatar da hangen nesan sa na juyin juya halin zamantakewar al'umma a tattalin arziki.
Mista McDonnell ya bayyana aniyarsa ta mayar da makamashi daga Shugabannin Anonymous da kuma Masana a kamfanonin samar da kayayyaki.
Shadow Chancellor din na shirin cewa masu hannun jari na yanzu a kamfanonin samar da ruwa ba za su iya komawa ga hannun jarin su ba, saboda gwamnatin Labour za ta iya yin "yankan-kashi" bisa laifukan da ake gani.
