Menene bikin Global Citizen kuma menene ya yi don rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, za a yi bikin kiɗa na shekara-shekara na Global Citizen a birnin New York, wanda ke nuna wasu taurari masu ban sha'awa da kuma wata manufa mai ban sha'awa don kawo ƙarshen talauci a duniya.
Bikin na Global Citizen na shekara ta bakwai, yana maraba da dubban mutane da za su taru a Central Park don su more ba kawai masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma kuma don su kara wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin bikin, wanda shine kawo karshen matsanancin talauci a shekarar 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen wanda aka kaddamar a shekarar 2012 ya kasance wani bangare na shirin Global Poverty, wata kungiya ta kasa da kasa da ke kokarin kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta (idan ba ka son biyan tikitin VIP) masu ziyara dole ne su kammala jerin ayyuka ko ayyuka kamar aikin sa kai, aika imel ga shugaban duniya, yin waya ko wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da burin kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar da Global Citizen ta samu shekaru 12 kafin ta cimma burinta?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ga mutane ta hanyar yin wasa kyauta da gaske ne ta hanyar shawo kan su su nemi aiki, ko kuwa wani abu ne da ake kira "clicktivism" - mutane da suke ganin cewa ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takarda ta yanar gizo ko kuma aika tweet za su kawo canji?
Global Citizen ta ce tun 2011 ta samu fiye da mutane miliyan 19 da suka raba shafinta, suna kokarin cimma burin su.
Ya ce, waɗannan ayyuka sun sa shugabannin duniya su sanar da alkawura da ayyuka na fiye da dala biliyan 37 da za su shafi rayukan mutane biliyan 2.25 a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta sanar da alkawura 390 da sanarwar da suka samo asali daga ayyukanta, wanda aƙalla dala biliyan 10 aka riga aka biya ko kuma an ba da kuɗin.
Ƙungiyar ta kimanta cewa, har zuwa yanzu, kuɗin da aka tanada ya shafi mutane kusan miliyan 649 a dukan duniya.
Muhimman alkawuran sun hada da Power of Nutrition, wani hadin gwiwar masu zuba jari da masu gudanar da ayyukan Birtaniya da suka yi alkawarin "taimaka yara su girma zuwa ga cikakkiyar damar su", suna mai bada alkawarin bayar da dala miliyan 35 ga Rwanda domin taimakawa wajen kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a yankin bayan karbar tweets sama da 4,700 daga Global Citizens.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da tallafi, gwamnatocin kasa da kuma 'yan kasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya sanya rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a matsayin sanarwa a tarihi", in ji Tracey Ullman, jakadan aikin Power of Nutrition, a lokacin wani taron jama'a a London a watan Afrilu na shekarar 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan gudanar da ayyuka sama da 5,000 da suka bukaci Burtaniya ta inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga mata da yara, gwamnatin ta sanar da kudaden da za ta samar wa shirin Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai mata da yara miliyan biyar da taimakon abinci mai gina jiki.
A amsa ga wata tambaya da aka fi yi a shafinta, ta ce, "Me ya sa kake tsammanin za mu iya kawo ƙarshen matsanancin talauci?"
Global Citizen ya amsa: "Za mu yi tafiya mai tsawo da wuya - wani lokaci za mu fadi kuma mu kasa.
Amma kamar manyan manufofin 'yancin jama'a da kuma na 'yancin nuna wariyar launin fata, za mu yi nasara domin tare muna da ƙarfi.
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Monae suna cikin wadanda za su yi wasan kwaikwayon a wannan shekara a New York, wanda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su yi.
Amurka na iya amfani da rundunar sojin ruwanta wajen hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida
Washington na iya amfani da rundunar sojin ruwa idan ya dace don hana shigowar makamashin Rasha zuwa kasuwannin da suka hada da yankin Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta ruwaito.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa, shigar Rasha cikin Syria - musamman inda take aiki a kan gayyatar da gwamnatin halal ta yi - ya zama hujja don bincika sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Ina ganin dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne domin suna son su yi amfani da makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a gabashin Turai, a kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma bisa ga sanarwar hukuma, akwai hanyoyin da za a bi don magance wannan.
"Amurka tana da damar yin hakan tare da taimakon sojojin ruwanmu, don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin teku suna buɗe kuma idan ya zama dole, an toshe su, don tabbatar da cewa makamashin su ba ya zuwa kasuwa", in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi magana ne ga masu halartar taron da Ƙungiyar Masu Amfani da Wutar Lantarki ta shirya, wata ƙungiya mai zaman kanta da ake kira "Muryar Masu Amfani da Wutar Lantarki" a Amirka.
Ya kwatanta yadda Washington ke hulda da Rasha da Iran, kuma ya ce sun yi daidai da juna.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki ga Iran da Rasha ya fi ko ƙasa da zuba jari a cikin ko maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yayin da yake nuni da Rasha a matsayin mai "ma'ana guda" mai tattalin arziki mai dogaro da man fetur.
Sanarwar ta zo ne saboda gwamnatin Trump na kan aikin bunkasa fitar da iskar gas dinta zuwa Turai, kuma ta maye gurbin Rasha da wani abu mai rahusa ga masu amfani da Turai.
Don haka, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, suna kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga aikin "Nord Stream 2" wanda Trump ya ce ya sanya Berlin ta zama "tafin hannun Moscow".
Moscow ta sha jaddada cewa, aikin Nord Stream 2 mai darajar dala biliyan 11, wanda aka tsara don ninka karfin aikin da ake da shi zuwa miliyan biliyan 110 ne, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ya ce, ana nuna cewa, hamayya da Washington ke yi da wannan aikin, na tattalin arziki ne, kuma misali ne na rashin adalci.
"Ina ganin muna da ra'ayin cewa ba za a iya amfani da makamashi a matsayin kayan aiki ba don matsa lamba kuma ya kamata masu amfani su sami damar zaɓar mai ba da kayayyaki", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Aleksandr Novak bayan ganawa da Ministan Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a watan Satumba a Moscow.
Amurka ta dauki mataki daga Jamus, wanda ya sake tabbatar da jajircewar sa ga aikin.
Babbar kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, BDI, ta bukaci Amurka da ta guji manufofin makamashi na EU da yarjejeniyar biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala idan wata kasa ta uku ta tsoma baki a samar da makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus (BDI), bayan ganawar da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren ta yi alkawarin duba takarar shugaban kasa na 2020, in ji Sanata daga Massachusetts
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta yi nazari sosai kan takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben tsakiyar shekara.
A lokacin taron na majalisa a Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ta tabbatar da cewa tana tunanin tsayawa takara.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su zo Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, ciki har da matsayi mafi girma na mata", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
