A cewar shugaban kamfanin John Bruce, manufar aikin Inrupt ita ce kawo albarkatu, aiyuka da kuma basira don taimakawa dandalin Solid ya zama mai amfani ga kowa.
Kamfanin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro wanda IBM ta saya, wasu ma'aikatan da ke aiki a kan aikin sun haɗa kai a kan aikin, da kuma al'umma na masu shirye-shirye masu sa kai.
