Lt. Col. Reverend Bernard Vann ya sami lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 a lokacin da yake kai hari a Bellenglis da Lehaucourt.
Amma, bayan kwana huɗu, wani ɗan bindiga ya kashe shi, kuma bai taɓa sanin cewa ya sami lambar yabo mafi girma a ƙasar Britaniya ba.
