Trump ya ce ba zai fi son ya saki Rosenstein ba, amma sai aka jinkirta taron don kada ya kai ga zaman kotun majalisa inda Kavanaugh da daya daga cikin matan da suka zarge shi da cin zarafin mata, Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, suka gabatar da shaidar.
A ranar Juma'a, Trump ya umarci FBI ta gudanar da bincike kan zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh, lamarin da ya sake jinkirta cikakken zaben majalisar dattawa.
