Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a lokacin girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da kuma tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na Indonesia ranar Juma'a, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu, in ji jami'an.
Tun da yake ba a iya samun bayanai ba, rundunar agaji ba ta samu bayanai daga yankin Donggala ba, wanda ke arewacin Palu, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
An kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 daga Palu bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da garin Palu da kuma yankin Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Central Sulawesi, wanda ke a ƙarshen bakin tekun a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, kuma yawansa ya kai mutane 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin da birnin yake bikin cika shekara 40 da kafuwarsa, girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka addabe shi.
Donggala shi ne regency da ke kan iyakar kilomita 300 (180 miles) a gabar tekun arewa maso yammacin Sulawesi.
A cikin 2017, Regency, yanki na yanki, yana da yawan jama'a 299,200.
Babban bangarorin tattalin arzikin lardin na Sulawesi na Tsakiya shine kamun kifi da noma, musamman a yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Akwai ma'adinai na nickel a lardin, amma galibi yana da ƙarfi a Morowali a gefen tekun tsibirin Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami ya addabi Palu da Donggala.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya sake afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, inda ya yi sanadin mutuwar mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake kira Pacific Ring of Fire kuma tana yawan samun girgizar ƙasa.
Ga jerin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, ta haifar da tsunami da ya afkawa kasashe 14 inda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a lardin Aceh.
2005: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Mutane da yawa sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afka kudu da tsibirin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta jawo tsunami da ya kai ga gaɓar tekun kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afka kusa da Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 suka rasa rayukansu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, kusa da Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai saurin girgiza yankin Pidie Jaya a lardin Aceh, ya haifar da bala'i da fargaba, saboda yana tunatar da mutane game da mummunar tasirin girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Ba a sami tsunami a wannan lokacin ba, amma sama da mutane 100 sun mutu sa'ad da gine-gine suka rushe.
